## Overview

This repository contains NixOS flake configurations for **{{ blueprint_repo_context.all_hosts | length }} VMs** in the infrastructure.

All configurations are generated from Ansible inventory (`inventory/{{ blueprint_repo_context.env }}/host_vars/*.yml`) and follow the "Single Point of Truth" principle.

