## Quick Start

### 1. Initialize Repository (First Time Only)

```bash
# Initialize SOPS keys (if not already done)
cd secrets && ./init.sh
```

### 2. Validate Configurations

```bash
nix flake check
```

### 3. Deploy to a Host

```bash
# Deploy from this repository
nixos-rebuild switch --flake .#<hostname> --target-host <hostname>

# Example: Deploy to {{ blueprint_repo_context.all_hosts.keys() | first }}
nixos-rebuild switch --flake .#{{ blueprint_repo_context.all_hosts.keys() | first }} --target-host {{ blueprint_repo_context.all_hosts.keys() | first }}
```

